ps://www.instagram.com/p/B4uErEzDnuA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uErEzDnuA%2F&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B50arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=8372c71f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4uErEzDnuA%2F&h=7737fdb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4uErEzDnuA/</a><br />\n<br />\n如遇意外，敢問學校的第三者保險是否涵蓋，以及校方能否承擔學生人命傷亡的責任？<br />\n<br />\n基於保障學生安全，作為貴校學校的家長，督請 貴校考慮自行安排停課。期望 貴校盡早作出決定，讓家長有足夠時間安排人手照顧子女。"},{"pid":"0edf4222be4fe476d05fdadfd694cb687e0ed54b","tid":1707155,"uid":322203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"要求全港學校停課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712211</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}